quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  37,145,"Nítorí náà, A jù ú sí orí ilẹ́ gban̄sasa létí omi. Ó sì jẹ́ aláìlera"
  37,146,A sì mú igi Yẹƙtīn hù jáde láti ṣíji bò ó
  37,147,A tún rán an níṣẹ́ sí ọ̀kẹ́ márùn-ún (ènìyàn) tàbí kí wọ́n lékún sí i
  37,148,Wọ́n gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. A sì fún wọn ní ìgbádùn títí di ìgbà díẹ̀
  37,149,"Bi wọ́n léèrè wò pé: \"Ṣé Olúwa rẹ l’ó ni àwọn ọmọbìnrin, tiwọn sì ni ọmọkùnrin"
  37,150,"Tàbí A dá àwọn mọlāika ní obìnrin, tí àwọn sì jẹ́ ẹlẹ́rìí"
  37,151,"Gbọ́, nínú irọ́ wọn ni pé dájúdájú wọ́n ń wí pé"
  37,152,"Allāhu bímọ.\" Dájúdájú òpùrọ́ ni wọ́n"
  37,153,Ṣé (Allāhu) ṣẹ̀ṣà àwọn ọmọbìnrin lórí àwọn ọmọkùnrin ni
  37,154,Kí l’ó ń ṣe yín tí ẹ fi ń dájọ́ báyìí
  37,155,Ṣé ẹ ò níí lo ìrántí ni
  37,156,Tàbí ẹ ní ẹ̀rí t’ó yanjú lọ́wọ́ ni
  37,157,Ẹ mú tírà yín wà nígbà náà tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo
  37,158,Wọ́n tún fi ìbátan sáààrin (Allāhu) àti àlùjànnú! Àwọn àlùjànnú sì ti mọ̀ pé dájúdájú wọ́n kúkú máa mú àwọn wá sínú Iná ni
  37,159,Mímọ́ ni fún Allāhu tayọ ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ròyìn (Rẹ̀)
  37,160,"Àfi àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,161,Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin àti n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún (lẹ́yìn Allāhu)
  37,162,ẹ ò lè fi ṣi ẹnì kan kan lọ́nà
  37,163,àfi ẹni tí ó bá fẹ́ wọ inú iná Jẹhīm
  37,164,Kò sí ẹnì kan nínú àwa (mọlāika) àfi kí ó ní ibùdúró tí wọ́n ti mọ̀
  37,165,"Dájúdájú àwa, a kúkú wà ní ọ̀wọ̀ọ̀wọ́"
  37,166,"Àti pé dájúdájú àwa, àwa kúkú ni olùṣàfọ̀mọ́ (fún Allāhu)"
  37,167,Wọ́n kúkú ń wí pé
  37,168,Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé dájúdájú a bá ní (tírà) ìrántí kan nínú (àwọn tírà) àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́
  37,169,"dájúdájú àwa ìbá jẹ́ ẹrúsìn Allāhu, àwọn ẹni ẹ̀ṣà"
  37,170,Ṣùgbọ́n wọ́n ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú (Allāhu). Láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀
  37,171,"Dájúdájú ọ̀rọ̀ Wa ti ṣíwájú fún àwọn ẹrúsìn Wa, àwọn Òjíṣẹ́"
  37,172,"Dájúdájú àwọn, àwọn l’a kúkú máa ṣàrànṣe fún"
  37,173,"Àti pé dájúdájú àwọn ọmọ ogun Wa, àwọn kúkú ni olùborí"
  37,174,"Nítorí náà, ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn fún ìgbà díẹ̀"
  37,175,"Àti pé máa wò wọ́n níran ná, àwọn náà ń bọ̀ wá ríran wò"
  37,176,Ṣé ìyà Wa ni wọ́n ń wá pẹ̀lú ìkánjú
  37,177,"Nígbà tí ó bá sọ̀kalẹ̀ sí agboolé wọn, òwúrọ̀ ọjọ́ náà yó sì burú fún àwọn ẹni-akìlọ̀-fún"
  37,178,Kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn títí di ìgbà kan ná
  37,179,"Àti pé máa wò wọ́n níran ná, àwọn náà ń bọ̀ wá ríran wò"
  37,180,"Mímọ́ ni fún Olúwa rẹ, Olúwa agbára, tayọ ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ròyìn (Rẹ̀)"
  37,181,Kí àlàáfíà máa bá àwọn Òjíṣẹ́
  37,182,"Gbogbo ọpẹ́ ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá"
  38,1,"Sọ̄d. (Allāhu búra pẹ̀lú) al-Ƙur’ān, tírà ìrántí"
  38,2,Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ àwọn t’ó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ wà nínú ìgbéraga àti ìyapa (òdodo)
  38,3,"Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìran tí A ti parẹ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Nígbà náà, wọ́n kígbe tòò nígbà tí kò sí ibùsásí kan"
  38,4,"Wọ́n ṣèèmọ̀ pé olùkìlọ̀ kan nínú wọn wá bá wọn. Àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ sì wí pé: \"Èyí ni òpìdán, òpùrọ́"
  38,5,Ṣé ó máa sọ àwọn òrìṣà di Ọlọ́hun Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo tí A óò máa jọ́sìn fún ni? Dájúdájú èyí mà ni n̄ǹkan ìyanu
  38,6,"Àwọn aṣíwájú nínú wọn sì lọ (káàkiri láti wí fún àwọn ọmọlẹ́yìn wọn) pé: \"Ẹ máa bá (ìbọ̀rìṣà) lọ, kí ẹ sì dúró ṣinṣin ti àwọn òrìṣà yín. Dájúdájú èyí (jíjẹ́ ọ̀kan ṣoṣo Allāhu) ni n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń gbà lérò (láti fi pa àwọn òrìṣà yín run)"
  38,7,"Àwa kò gbọ́ èyí nínú ẹ̀sìn ìkẹ́yìn (ìyẹn, ẹ̀sìn kristiẹniti) . Èyí kò jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe àdápa irọ́"
  38,8,"Ṣé Wọ́n sọ Ìrántí kalẹ̀ fún un láààrin wa ni?\" Rárá, wọ́n wà nínú iyèméjì nípa Ìrántí Mi (tí Mo sọ̀kalẹ̀ ni). Rárá, wọn kò tí ì tọ́ ìyà Mi wò ni"
  38,9,"Tàbí (ṣé) àwọn ni wọ́n ni àwọn àpótí ọ̀rọ̀ Olúwa rẹ, Alágbára, Ọlọ́rẹ"
  38,10,"Tàbí tiwọn ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti ohun tí ń bẹ láààrin méjèèjì? Tí ó bá rí bẹ́ẹ̀, kí wọn wá àwọn ọ̀nà láti fi gùnkè wá (bá Wa)"
  38,11,A máa ṣẹ́gun ọmọ ogun t’ó wà níbẹ̀ yẹn nínú ọmọ ogun oníjọ
  38,12,"Àwọn ìjọ Nūh, ìjọ ‘Ād àti Fir‘aon, eléèkàn, wọ́n pe òdodo nírọ́ ṣíwájú wọn"
  38,13,"Ìjọ Thamūd, ìjọ Lūt àti àwọn ará ’Aekah, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn (tún ni) àwọn ìjọ (t’ó pe òdodo nírọ́)"
  38,14,"Kò sí ẹnì kan nínú wọn tí kò pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, ìyà Mi sì kò lé wọn lórí"
  38,15,"Àwọn wọ̀nyí kò retí kiní kan tayọ igbe ẹyọ kan, tí kò níí sí ìdápadà (tàbí ìdádúró) kan fún un (t’ó bá dé)"
  38,16,"Wọ́n wí pé: \"Olúwa wa, yára fi ìwé iṣẹ́ wa (àti ẹ̀san wa) lé wa lọ́wọ́ ṣíwájú Ọjọ́ ìṣírò-iṣẹ́"
  38,17,"Ṣe sùúrù lórí n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń sọ. Kí o sì ṣèrántí ìtàn ẹrúsìn Wa, (Ànábì) Dāwūd, alágbára. Dájúdájú ó jẹ́ olùronúpìwàdà"
  38,18,Dájúdájú Àwa tẹ àwọn àpáta lórí ba tí wọ́n ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ (fún Allāhu) ní àṣálẹ́ àti nígbà tí òòrùn bá yọ
  38,19,"Àti àwọn ẹyẹ náà, A kó wọn jọ fún un. Ìkọ̀ọ̀kan (wọn) ń tẹ̀lé àṣẹ rẹ̀ (láti ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu)"
  38,20,Àti pé A fún ìjọba rẹ̀ ní agbára. A sì fún un ní ipò Ànábì àti ẹ̀kọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ àti ìdájọ́